Welcome to Invasion of the Mutant Space Bats of Doom, Shareware Version,
distributed by Pop Software. You should have these files:

 READ.ME          Initial information 
 BATS.EXE         The game
 INFO.EXE         Viewer for the this documentation
 BATS.DOC         This documentation                               
 BATS.DAT         The game's data                                  
 AUTOFORM.EXE     Allows you to fill-out ORDER.FRM before printing it
 ORDER.FRM        Blank order form                                       
 FILES.DOC        A copy of this file list                         
 VENDOR.DOC       Info about distributing these files              
 VGAIDEMO.EXE     A demo of VGA Interludes                         
 HELP.ME          See this file if you have trouble or find bugs
 FILE_ID.DIZ      This game's text description                      

If any files are missing, contact us to receive the complete BATS.ZIP.

Please share BATS.ZIP by giving it to your friends and uploading it 
to your favorite BBS. For information about other types of distribution,
please see VENDOR.DOC.

The files BATS.KEY, BATS.JOY, BATS.TOP, and BATS.SET are created when
you play or configure the game. AUTO.FRM is created with AUTOFORM. 
You should not distribute these files, and if they've been passed along 
to you, delete them before playing for the first time.

